# This file-Maven-repo is committed so a clone of termtastic alone can build
# against darkness-toolkit with no sibling checkout. Refresh it from the toolkit
# with `./gradlew :toolkit-core:publishAllPublicationsToTermtasticLibsRepoRepository`
# (and the toolkit-store/web/compose equivalents).
#
# Keep .pom, .module, and the binary artifacts (.klib/.jar/.aar) — those are what
# Gradle resolves. Ignore the regenerated noise so republishes produce clean diffs.

# Re-include .klib artifacts: the repo-root .gitignore ignores *.klib globally,
# but the iOS/JS toolkit variants are published as .klib and MUST be committed.
!*.klib

# Regenerated noise — not needed to resolve fixed-version deps from a file repo.
*.md5
*.sha1
*.sha256
*.sha512
maven-metadata.xml*
*-sources.jar
*-kotlin-tooling-metadata.json
